{"tw": {"2696060": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "妖精調教儀式", "steam_appid": 2696060, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆故事 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一個名為「淫神教」的教團，為了要解開他們所崇拜淫神的封印，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >遵照著聖旨在世界各地中去捕獲祭品。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有一天，你被一個神秘的教團綁架並囚禁起來。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >身旁的是與你一樣被擄獲來的可愛妖精少女。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你必須跟著妖精少女，進行長達七天的性愛儀式，提供精氣來解開淫神的封印。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果不照做就無法逃脫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696060/extras/16777f0ec57918489cd84262182ab317.poster.avif?t=1762767388\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696060/extras/16777f0ec57918489cd84262182ab317.webm?t=1762767388\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696060/extras/16777f0ec57918489cd84262182ab317.mp4?t=1762767388\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆遊戲玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在這與妖精的七天性愛儀式中，選擇卡片所提示性愛項目進行儀式。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透過配置卡片與觸摸遊戲來推進遊戲故事劇情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >透過累積的行動點（AP）來強化你的能力，反覆進行儀式直至實現教團的目標。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696060/extras/fc7f49ca3715a540a253cad1a1463e8c.avif?t=1762767388\" width=600 height=450 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆角色</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2696060/extras/716ac235865e980c33027e4ed96d2652.avif?t=1762767388\" width=600 height=350 /></span><strong>Sophie</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >種族：精靈</p>